Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:02.87,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Dun-da-da-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.99,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:07.00,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Azusa, Witch of the Highlands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.90,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,you are to be awarded the \NDemon Medal of Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, what did you show \Nup out of the blue for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:16.96,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Could you try to sound a little happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:19.46,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's a prestigious award \Nbestowed only upon those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:23.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,who are loved by many demons and \Nhave made a drastic difference
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.39,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,by giving bright hope to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:28.73,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You recently ended the conflict \Nbetween the Red Dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.82,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,and the Blue Dragons that \Nhad lasted for generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.88,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,and made them agree permanently to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:37.42,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You were recognized for that, and you \Nget the medal in the peace category.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's just how it ended \Nup working out, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.74,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Of course, you will accept it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.22,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That's a great honor, Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.14,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Way to go, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.02,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.02,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I'm proud to be your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:54.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, then, I'll gratefully accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.95,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The ceremony will be held in three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You should all attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.19,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I'll come to collect you \Nshortly before it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.85,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The Demon Realm. \NThat's where the ceremony is held.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.81,Main,All,0,0,0,,The Demon Realm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:10.15,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.34,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,There's no need to get so up in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.24,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Most demons are well-bred \Nladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:19.04,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The ones who wanted to destroy humanity, \Nlike in olden days, are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.38,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,As long as you show the bare minimum \Nof good etiquette, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Bare minimum...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:25.71,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,...of good etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:31.51,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,What?
