Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.65,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,A demon ceremony gives me \Nnothing but bad feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I develop a \Nstomachache on just that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.02,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You're gonna fake being sick, Halkara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:24.59,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,No, no! I just have a feeling \Nthat, by total coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,my stomach is going to hurt that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.32,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You might as well give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.84,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Missing such a prestigious ceremony \Nwould bring shame to the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.63,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:40.15,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I will attend with the resolution of someone \Nplanning to leap off the Kyalar Spire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.08,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.87,Main - Top,Falfa,0,0,0,,What's the Kyalar Spire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.43,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess this world has its own \Nidiom that means "take a plunge,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:49.45,Main - Top,Shalsha,0,0,0,,A famous building of great historical value, \Nmaking it an important cultural asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.15,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,like "jump off the stage at Kiyomizu."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.51,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, what shall \Nwe wear to the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.51,Main - Top,Falfa,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:53.84,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Why don't we just wear what we \Nwore to the dragon's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.81,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Uh, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:01.86,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,You really think it's okay for a ghost \Nlike me to attend such a major ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're part of my family now, Rosalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.16,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You'll need a dress, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Want to go to the village and have one made?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.82,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,No way. I'm a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.42,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how to change my outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You can't take that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.30,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I can't even touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.91,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This poses an unexpected problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You think there are stores \Nthat sell clothes for ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.79,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That kind of business isn't even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.70,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Ghosts don't have any money, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true business owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.82,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,If you need a scholar specializing \Nin ghosts, I recently met one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.03,Main,Scholar,0,0,0,,Now, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:50.34,Main,Scholar,0,0,0,,Ghosts are spirits that have \Nremained in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.13,Main,Scholar,0,0,0,,with an appearance close to \Nwhat they looked like in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:56.55,Main,Scholar,0,0,0,,What looks like clothing is \Nonly a part of that spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.75,Main,Scholar,0,0,0,,It is not possible to change \Na spirit's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.16,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:06.39,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Shalsha knows people like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:12.02,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,So your clothes are a memory \Nof when you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.14,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I did wear \Nstuff like this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.81,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Maybe if you envision other \Nclothes strongly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.99,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,you can change into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's not something we can help with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.04,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister, it's okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.93,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,What's impossible is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.14,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I'm just fine sticking with this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:38.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Rosalie,	 you think everything's fine \Nif you can just endure it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But just enduring isn't always a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:46.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Besides, you want to wear a dress to the \Nceremony with the rest of us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.13,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,If it's possible... I'd like to wear one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.39,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then we shouldn't give up. Let's find a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.55,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,How, though? Doing that would be like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:08.70,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's right. I have the Create Magic skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.35,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's no spell that can \Nchange a ghost's clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.70,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,which means I just need to create one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.33,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Time to show off what a cheat witch can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:18.98,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.13,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Uh, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.87,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Showing me a real dress won't help. \NI can't put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:30.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Rosalie, take a good look at this \Ndress and ingrain it in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:35.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then envision yourself wearing \Nthis dress at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:42.24,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister, if you're making this some kind of \N"those who believe shall be saved" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:45.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I don't think I like being treated \Nlike an occultist by a ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.39,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No, that's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Just believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.46,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.45,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister... Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:03.22,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I will repay your fiery passion in kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There, all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:28.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.94,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Okay, Sister! I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Land of the living, land of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Shine upon the darkness \Nbetween the two realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:42.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and allow this outstretched \Nhand to reach the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.00,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Work, magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Change, Rosalie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.69,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.51,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I could even go to a ball \Nwithout any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.26,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Rosalie, you look so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.94,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You're just like a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.38,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Except the way you speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.39,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.83,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! \NWhat kind of magic did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I basically tried to enhance my image of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,in a way that wouldn't \Ndamage your spirit body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.56,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Your image of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.48,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister, would it be possible \Nto do a little fine tuning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? You want to add something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:37.94,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.39,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Please put "Rosalie Is Here" on my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.90,Narration,Azusa,0,0,0,,Soon, it was time to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.48,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Is it a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.98,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It bears a slight resemblance \Nto us Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.15,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I really hope the demons don't hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.57,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please don't hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.59,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.20,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I have arrived to collect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.86,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,At last, the time came to depart \Nfor the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:15.14,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A Leviathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:18.63,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.28,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It is a large type of demon that can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.18,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,This is the one who will carry \Nyou to the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.95,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,There's a big building on its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.86,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Are we dreaming or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.41,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's like a luxury liner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.91,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Not entirely correct, but not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.41,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Let me show you the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.01,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,This is the VIP guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.46,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Klik-klak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.68,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,This is the large bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.80,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Also, this bath—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing \Nwhen you're on the clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:55.68,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.80,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.56,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.41,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.26,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I am Vania the Leviathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.64,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Get dressed before you introduce yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.19,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.90,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Now, allow me to explain the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.63,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,This large bath is a demon spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Demon spring? Is that a demons' hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.89,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Indeed. It feels slippery on the \Nskin and is great for beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.75,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:24.21,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If you stay in for several \Nhours, you'll melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:25.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's scary! And bad for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.34,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Only after several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.12,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,No one stays in the bath that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:35.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Halkara, please be careful not \Nto get in this bath alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Nobody trusts me at all, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.11,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't Leviathans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:48.38,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Yes, the one you're riding right \Nnow is my older sister, Fatla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.10,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,We rotate the tasks of flying and \Nattending to guests in our human forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.76,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Vania is also in charge of your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:59.47,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Your meal today will have \Na focus on poultry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.98,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,The vegetables are carefully selected \Nfirst-class products, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.96,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.90,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Wow, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.70,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,By the way, Vania, you will write \Na letter of apology later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.83,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Please be lenient with me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.48,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,No. You will write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, what a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.86,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The buildings all look so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.59,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It looks so boundless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.02,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I believe I've shown you everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.86,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If you need anything, just let Vania know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:35.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But do we really deserve \Nsuch a glamorous reception?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Must you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.92,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That is just how incredible \Nyour accomplishment was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.77,Main - Top,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha, let's go look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:41.41,Main - Top,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.44,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You ended a long-lasting \Nconflict between Dragon clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.62,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Your name will go down in history for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:51.97,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Azusa, you can be a bit \Nmore proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I'll do my best not to \Nembarrass us at the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.20,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You have no ambition, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.97,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:09.12,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,This is a salad made with \Ntwenty types of vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, high luxury right from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I've never tasted anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:21.16,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,This is a potage made from mashed \NNorthern thick-shelled beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.14,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Cockatrice eggs wrapped in lettuce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.73,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,An omelette made from Roc eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.12,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,So light and runny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:35.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This might be the best egg \Ndish I've ever tasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.35,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I never knew there was \Nan omelette like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.34,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I still have much to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.64,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The difference in flavor is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.26,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,These ingredients are worth a \Nthousand times more than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.92,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,A thousand... times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If she somehow made anything \Nbad from these ingredients,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.19,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Vania would have to write \Nanother apology letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:57.19,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I can't slack off at all when \Nworking under Lady Beelzebub...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.68,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You're saying that after taking \Na bath while on the clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.58,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Vania, it really was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.29,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Klik-klak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:08.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The food was great, \Nand the bath is fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I was a little nervous about \Ngoing to the land of the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but I guess there was no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.91,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to feel that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:21.56,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I think this might turn out to be a \Nnice trip with no problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,When you say stuff like that, \Nit feels like another flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.19,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Come on, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.41,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,We're flying over an empty wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.99,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,The Demon Realm's still a ways off, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.28,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,The stars are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:58.95,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Even up this high, I'm still \Nnowhere near Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.23,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.58,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Hey, Sister Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:08.01,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I woke up for some reason, \Nso I thought I'd take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.34,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,You're headed in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.32,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I was so sleepy, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.63,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,And what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.18,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Just checking out the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.64,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,There's nothing to see at all, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:23.19,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,It's still totally new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:27.71,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,If I'd stayed a bound spirit, I never \Nwould've been able to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.07,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.64,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,And it's all because you made \Nthat building your factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.83,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I can't thank you and Sister enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.37,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I swear I'll repay this debt someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.84,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Don't trouble yourself with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.27,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,There are no debts between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:48.75,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,We're family now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master would \Ntell you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.66,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to the bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:08.13,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I feel as warm as if I'd just \Nbeen in the bath, too, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.91,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Morning, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Morning. You two are up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.37,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Halkara, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.29,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,She wasn't there when we got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:26.60,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister Halkara came out in the middle of the \Nnight saying she was gonna take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.15,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,A bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.81,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Slither, slither.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.94,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:40.10,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I was so sleepy, I fell under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:44.06,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Everyone awake? We're about \Nto enter the Demon Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.81,Main - Top,Laika,0,0,0,,I didn't know what we'd do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.59,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:50.08,Main - Top,Halkara,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.53,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Do you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:58.20,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The giant fortress city in the distance \Nis the royal capital Vanzeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.72,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You lot will first visit the \Npalace to meet the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.78,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,After that... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.71,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The ceremony is tomorrow, so I \Ncould show you around the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:14.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um, Beelzebub? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I said I could show you around the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.81,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Oh, about the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.83,Main,All,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.17,Main,All,0,0,0,,Demon King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:30.07,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\be2}Fortress City Vanzeld - Castle Town
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.40,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,There are many different races of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.67,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Some are just like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.60,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Some are similar to animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.64,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,They come in many shapes and sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:43.88,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,354)\be2}Vanzeld Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.90,Main - Top,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,We'll walk from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.59,Main - Top,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Don't worry about your things. \NVania will carry them in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um, Beelzebub...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do we absolutely have \Nto meet the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.81,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:56.08,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The Demon Medal of Honor is awarded \Nby the head of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:17:00.14,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Better to have your first audience \Nbeforehand than at the ceremony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.13,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Halkara! \NPlease try not to do anything silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:08.26,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I know. If I do, I'll probably be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:12.99,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,They'll skin me and then \Nthrow me into the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.99,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,No one's going to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:18.63,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If you insult our king, \NI'll throw you into the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.70,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm dead either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.17,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,It's like a maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.93,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's to confuse any enemies that \Nattack, so they can be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.61,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,A relic of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's so demon-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.45,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.22,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Can I just fake illness \Nfor the rest of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:38.78,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Actually, my stomach really \Nis starting to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.47,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Only because of all the walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.73,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Look, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.34,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The Demon King's chamber \Nis beyond this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.49,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,It's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Everyone, remember your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.65,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.86,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The Demon King is a friendly sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.20,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You can just act as you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.67,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,But, Beelzebub,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:05.45,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,no matter how careful I am, \NI usually mess things up regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.94,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Our king is big-hearted enough to \Nforgive even someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.69,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Let us pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.37,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.30,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.22,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Welcome to Vanzeld Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um... Hi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.50,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You're Azusa, the Witch \Nof the Highlands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.95,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.64,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Please shake my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.39,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.04,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, if we stand around here talking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:46.57,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,and keep the Demon King waiting, \Nit'll make a bad impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.17,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You must be Halkara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.89,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I drink Nutri-Spirit all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.53,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Please shake my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:58.09,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Ouch! That hurts! \NYour grip is much too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.89,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.59,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Here! Healing magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.53,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:10.06,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, but could you \Ngo elsewhere for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.65,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,We need to go and meet the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:19.88,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,We don't want him to say, \N"You're late! Off with the elf's head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.83,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Aw, the Demon King wouldn't \Nsay anything that mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.47,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, but you don't know that for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.96,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Friendly or not, his values may \Nbe very different from ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:34.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I must demonstrate proper manners \Nand hide my true nature to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.80,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I hope I can manage to fool him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.35,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You want to fool the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.85,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Not out of malice, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:44.80,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,But that's an important part of \Ninterpersonal relationships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um... Beelzebub?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's no one on the throne. \NWhere is the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.29,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Hm? Right in front of you, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.69,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'm the Demon King, Provat Pecora Allières.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.40,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I don't like towering over \Npeople when I meet them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.12,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,so I came down here to wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Right, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.53,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.21,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:18.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,All that stuff about fooling you and \Nhiding my nature was a figure of speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.03,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Halkara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:25.01,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to fake sick, \Nbut does your stomach hurt for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.41,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Illnesses start within.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.98,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It's possible she was focusing so much \Non faking sick that she really got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.39,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Cut her some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:36.33,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Wow, you were actually thinking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:40.36,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,No... I was only worried that \NI'd make some silly mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.92,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,King Plot Pecona Alias...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.61,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's King Provat Pecora Allières.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.68,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:51.68,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa! She keeps piling on \Nmore and more rude blunders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yes, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.48,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,There's no need to bow to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.72,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You're not one of my retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.94,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,So long as there's life in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.18,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I will never bring harm to any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.55,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.38,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Please raise your head, Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.19,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Right! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:14.91,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.07,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.17,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.19,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.54,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,My Demon King! Please stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.17,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pecoraaaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:34.29,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Her spirit's flown out of her! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.38,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Hallll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.24,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Halkara! I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.99,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,She's unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.14,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Get her to the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.52,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I don't know much about demon laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.34,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,but in human law, anyone who harms \Nroyalty is usually executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um... Beelzebub?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:56.85,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If I'd known she would do this, \NI would've let her fake being sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.01,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Halkara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.31,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,will be executed.
